    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dense, yellow wood of the species Platanus occidentalis, having a fine texture that is similar to maple. It is used for furniture, butcher blocks, chairs, musical instruments, interior finishes, and cabinetry..</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
